SYNOPSIS (OPTIONAL)
===================
   int db_close(intÂ handle)

DESCRIPTION
===========
   Close the server-connection with the handle handle(E) Return the handle-
   number on success.

   The function is available only if the driver is compiled with mySQL 
   support. In that case, __MYSQL__ is defined.

   The efun triggers a privilege violation ("mysql", "db_close").

HISTORY
=======
   - introduced (3.2.9)
   - changed (3.2.11) -- adds the privilege violation.

